1
00:00:05,340 --> 00:00:08,430
(Yuki and I... we actually kissed.)

2
00:00:14,350 --> 00:00:16,390
What... are you doing?

3
00:00:16,390 --> 00:00:19,640
(Could it be... he's as hung up on it as I am?)

4
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:20,980
The school festival is coming up.

5
00:00:21,840 --> 00:00:24,520
I was thinking about how
to make you look more like a "prince."

6
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:27,690
(This guy... he's acting way too normal!)

7
00:00:29,400 --> 00:00:33,870
Makoto, you've got something on your face.

8
00:00:33,870 --> 00:00:34,990
Where?

9
00:00:34,990 --> 00:00:36,580
No, the other side.

10
00:00:37,620 --> 00:00:39,080
No, right here.

11
00:00:39,080 --> 00:00:40,330
What was that for?!

12
00:00:40,330 --> 00:00:41,750
What?

13
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:43,790
Sorry. Was it that bad?

14
00:00:44,750 --> 00:00:47,920
It's not that I hated it, it's just...

15
00:00:48,170 --> 00:00:51,720
(Great...
I'm the only one making a big deal out of this.)

16
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:53,930
(If I'm like this...
how can I let him do my makeup?)
